title: Hermes_test
---
<<Fade "#000000" 1 0 0.6>>        // fade back in
//<<PlayAudio "Romance">>  
<<PlayMusic "Hermes_Theme>>
<<Scene "lounge bg draft 3">>
<<Act "Aelius" "Aelius 3_4s" "left" "bottom" #674ea7>>
Aelius: Hey, welcome in.

<<Act "Hermes" "Hermes 3_4" "right" "bottom" #023020>>
Hermes: Hi there, can I get a—

Hermes: Wait, you're new here.
Aelius: Yes, my name's Aelius, I'm the new cook. Hestia hired me. Today's my first day.
Hermes: Well hello then, Aelius. I'm Hermes.
Hermes: But I assume you already guessed that.
-> It's nice to meet you, sir.
    Aelius: It's nice to meet you, sir.
    Hermes: None of that formality needed! But it's nice to meet you too.
    Hermes: I'm in a hurry, kid — not much time to chat. Could you whip me up a Lotus Parfait? Quickly, please.
    Aelius: You got it. I'll do my best.
-> I gathered, from the hat and sandals.
    Aelius: I gathered, from the hat and sandals.
    Hermes: Good catch. You're the observant type, eh?
    Hermes: I'm in a hurry, kid — not much time to chat. Could you whip me up a Lotus Parfait? Quickly, please.
    Aelius: You got it. I'll do my best.
-> Obviously.
    Aelius: Obviously.
    Hermes: Not the one for small talk I take it? Suit yourself.
    Hermes: I'm in a hurry, kid — not much time to chat. Could you whip me up a Lotus Parfait? Quickly, please.
    Aelius: You got it. I'll do my best.
-> I had my suspicions.
    Aelius: I had my suspicions.
    Hermes: (Sarcastic) <i>Very<i> clever of you.
    Hermes: I'm in a hurry, kid — not much time to chat. Could you whip me up a Lotus Parfait? Quickly, please.
    Aelius: You got it. I'll do my best.

<<StartCooking "LotusParfait">>

<<jump Hermes_test_Success>>
===

title: Hermes_test_Success
---
<<Scene "lounge bg draft 3">>
<<Act "Aelius" "Aelius 3_4s" "left" "bottom" #674ea7>>
<<PlayMusic "Hermes_Theme>>
Aelius: Got your Lotus Parfait ready as fast as I could.
Aelius: <i>(Hopefully this goes better than the other two…)</i>
Aelius: Or at least better than Zeus. *sigh*
Aelius: Hope you like it.

<<Act "Hermes" "Hermes 3_4" "right" "bottom" #023020>>
Hermes: Thanks, Aelius. Looks great!
Hermes: Only wish I had time to sit and enjoy it.
Hermes: But duty calls. Messages to deliver, cattle to steal. You get the jist.

Aelius: … Yeah
Hermes: You're lookin' a litte down in the dumps. Rough first day?
-> It is, but you don't have to worry about it...
    Aelius: It is, but you don't have to worry about it..
    Hermes: Don't sweat it.
-> Yeah, it's not like I thought it would be.
    Aelius: Yeah, it's not like I thought it would be.
    Hermes: What'd you think it'd be?
    Aelius: I figured the customers might be a bit more polite.
-> It's none of your business.
    Aelius: It's none of your business.
    Hermes: Figured I might as well ask.
    Aelius: It's fine, I'm fine.
-> You could say that.
    Aelius: You could say that.
    Hermes: I know I'd be spot on.
Hermes: Let me guess — Zeus stopped in.
Aelius: How did you know?
Hermes: Call it godly intuition. 
Hermes: But honestly, it's easy to tell. He's very good at ruffling newcomers' feathers.
Aelius: I just, well... He didn't seem to want me here. I cooked his food to perfection.
Hermes: Aelius, right? Listen up. People like Zeus are just some honor and glory loving dudes.
Hermes: Just ignore him. Do your best. Show him you're up to snuff.
Aelius: It's not that easy-
Hermes: I really gotta be going. Can't be late on these messages.
Hermes: I'll see you around!
Aelius: Well, that was... better, I guess.

<<Hide "Hermes">>

<<set $hermes_day1_done = true>>
<<jump Hephaestus_Intro>>

<<wait 2>>
<<QuitGame>>
===


